						</li>
						<li>
							<span class="check">‚úì</span>
							<span><strong>Ongoing Support:</strong> Continuous guidance throughout your AI journey</span>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span class="check">‚úì</span>
							<span><strong>24-hour Response:</strong> Quick response to all inquiries</span>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span class="check">‚úì</span>
							<span><strong>Free Consultation:</strong> Initial consultation at no cost</span>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Call to Action -->
	<section class="cta-section">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Ready to Transform Your Business with AI?</h2>
			<p>
				Join the growing number of Hong Kong businesses leveraging AI for competitive advantage. 
				Let's discuss your AI transformation journey today.
			</p>
			<div class="cta-buttons">
				<a href="/about" class="button primary">
